column27: This book is addressed to the reader who wants, as an educated person, to have an outline of the present state of knowledge of the constituents of the material world; who has a logical cast of mind and wi ll follow a mathematical argument; but who may have little knowledge of physics and no intention of becoming deeply involved in the subject.
